description.en:
Hitorijime (You're All Mine) features NaPaTa’s signature leading ladies, but unlike the timidness of his past characters, these women need to be indulged in every bit of pleasure that fill their hunger. These girls might be a little pushy and needy but when the chips are down, these guys fold under the pressure at the first sight of their flushing faces and bare flesh.

(Source: Fakku)

1. Lunch Time / Ohirudoki (おひるどき); Comic Kairakuten 2016-04
2. I Wanna Buy a Kitty / Neko ga Itai (ねこかいたい); Comic Kairakuten 2016-09
3. Princess / Ohimesama (おひめさま); Comic Kairakuten 2017-12
4. Bride / Oyomesan (およめさん); Comic Kairakuten 2016-12
5. I Can Do it Myself / Hitori de Yarerumon ♡ (ひとりでヤれるもん♡); Comic Kairakuten 2017-08 + kakioroshi
6. Cat & I / Neko to. (猫と。); Comic Kairakuten 2018-08
7. Booty Call / Yobidashi (よびだし); Comic Kairakuten 2018-03 + kakioroshi
8. Sleepover Princess / Isuwari Princess (いすわりプリンセス); Comic Kairakuten 2019-03
9. Good Luck Charm / Omajinai (おまじない); Comic Kairakuten 2018-06
10. Appointment / Machiawase (まちあわせ); Comic Kairakuten 2017-04
11. Please, Senpai / Senpai, Onegai (せんぱい、おねがい); Comic Kairakuten 2018-12
12. After Bath Time / Ofuroagari (おふろあがり); Comic Kairakuten 2016-01
Continuation to the chapters Mikkai and Warui Ko
